Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.50,0:01:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother... Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.50,0:01:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MOTHER...!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Beast Invasion\Nepisode 6\NThe Final Battle
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.58,0:02:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahoy! Ahoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.55,0:02:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here! The beach\NI've been dreaming of!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.01,0:02:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clear skies, blue coral reefs,\Nand all the sun you could want!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.27,0:02:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kayo. Isn't\Nthis island great?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.98,0:02:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I've always wanted\Nto go to one of these...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.98,0:02:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...little uncharted\Nouter islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.24,0:02:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, all right! I don't\Nwant you all wandering around!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.95,0:02:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Form up! Form up!\NFORM UP!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.16,0:02:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm going to check to\Nsee if there's any problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.29,0:03:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with our reservations and\Nthe room assignments.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.29,0:03:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So wait here until I get back.\NNo wandering off, understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.34,0:03:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.64,0:03:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Muneto. How far apart\Ndo you think they'll keep...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.64,0:03:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...us guys from the girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.31,0:03:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cuz we may just\Nhave a chance here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot.\NTo sneak out at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.28,0:03:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshioka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.65,0:03:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, women expect you\Nto do things like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in a carefree\Nsituation like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.99,0:03:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.37,0:03:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know so.\NSo, when do we break out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.08,0:03:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just like to\Nget down to business.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.96,0:03:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just been thinking\Nabout this trip...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.79,0:03:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...since they decided\Non it last month!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.75,0:03:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hold it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.01,0:03:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.02,0:04:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it great? Just the sort\Nof setting for two people...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.03,0:04:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to give in to a\Nromantic love adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.24,0:04:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Careful, Chika.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, even if those stupid\Nguys in our class don't come...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.79,0:04:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we've got some real\Nhunks on this island, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.91,0:04:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be taken up in a\Nsalt-scented embrace...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that'd be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.51,0:04:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Muneto?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo, do you want to take a\Nprivate trip out onto the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.97,0:04:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! It's a chance\Nfor us to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.27,0:04:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I've got the coolest\Nboat lined up for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.49,0:04:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.99,0:04:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:04:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.76,0:05:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fantastic! They look like\Nsomething from another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.14,0:05:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.81,0:05:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to get you in this\Nmood so we could really get close.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.77,0:05:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Careful, careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.11,0:05:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let that nasty little\Nguy spoil the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want this special feeling\Nto last a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo... Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.85,0:06:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.19,0:06:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.94,0:06:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother's scent! My Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.53,0:06:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's calling me...\NThe Demon Beast?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calling to me... No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.58,0:06:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.50,0:06:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ungyosai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit, it's Shinoda!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.88,0:06:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Kayo!\NKayo? Get in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.59,0:06:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:06:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shittin' me, Gramps?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an old, old story\Non this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.91,0:07:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.45,0:07:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go? Shinoda\Nwas looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what's got everybody\Nlooking so serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.59,0:07:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing there. That thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.26,0:07:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That islet has a beautiful\Nand sad legend behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard of the Untamagiruu\Nand the other nature spirits..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that are supposed to\Nlive on Okinawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.61,0:07:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But is this sea monster\None of them, Gramps?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might very well be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.53,0:07:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may just be an old legend...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but some girls on this\Nisland claim to have seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, what's the story?\NTell it to me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On this island, we believe\Nthat the souls of the dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:08:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...return after going to their\Nhome at the ends of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.93,0:08:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, a village girl found\Na strange creature on that islet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.31,0:08:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would have died without\Nsomeone to look after it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.98,0:08:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and she raised it as lovingly\Nas she would have her own child.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.28,0:08:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea monster grew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.62,0:08:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its ugliness became so great...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.62,0:08:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that the girl dared not\Nbring it home with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.38,0:08:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She knew that if the\Nadults on the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.63,0:08:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...discovered its existence,\Nthey would kill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, on rainy days and\Nwindy days as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.98,0:08:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the girl would go to the\Nislet and care for the creature...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.69,0:08:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...like it was her own child.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.70,0:09:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the night of a storm,\Nthe wounded monster lay dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As she nursed it,\Nit suddenly became aroused.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.09,0:09:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The poor girl,\Nhalf mad with grief...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.72,0:09:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...decided to satisfy its\Ndesire with her own body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The monster was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.84,0:10:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl's parents were furious\Nwhen she refused to tell them...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.01,0:10:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the name of the father of\Nthe child she now carried.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, they conspired with\Ntheir friends to kill the child.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.73,0:10:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you shame me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As she desperately tried to\Nprotect her monstrous child...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.83,0:11:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the villagers smashed it\Nto death before her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.16,0:11:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! NO!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.80,0:11:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the girl\Nrefused to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.51,0:11:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She set out upon the water,\Npursuing her child's soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.51,0:11:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to the ocean's end.\NShe never returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.81,0:11:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her father and the others,\Ntouched with pity for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...built a shrine to\Nher memory on the islet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.15,0:11:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then they prayed to the sea,\Nfearing its retribution.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.45,0:11:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.86,0:11:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That creature's supposed to\Nreturn to this island someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.45,0:11:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And perhaps the spirit of\Nthat girl, now reborn...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...awaits its return as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinda scary, but it's\Nstill a sad story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That little islet has a\Nweird legend attached to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.90,0:12:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now wait a second!\NHow can you be in the mood...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.94,0:12:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...after hearing\Nthat creepy story?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.57,0:12:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That has nothing\Nto do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.57,0:12:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some old superstition isn't gonna\Nget rid of this bulge in my shorts!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.54,0:12:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why do I have to\Ncome along with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.58,0:12:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your beef?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.17,0:12:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Running out on our\Nown is against the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.58,0:12:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the two of us,\Nwe're covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.63,0:12:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a happy\Nlittle adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.59,0:12:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.51,0:12:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God, I can practically\Nsmell the juice in 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.89,0:13:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ungyosai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.23,0:13:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.27,0:13:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't scare me\Nlike that, Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.90,0:13:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't sleep, so I\Nfigured I'd take a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.57,0:13:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow I doubt that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth! Believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.95,0:13:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After you and Voshioka said I\Nshould be out here on watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.62,0:13:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bet you were trying for\Na midnight rendezvous!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. Look, I happen to\Ncome from a temple family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go bad-mouthing people!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.29,0:13:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I'm to take you\Nat your word, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, if you can't\Nsleep, you can come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Night rounds. We have a duty to\Nprotect the ladies of the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.68,0:13:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.27,0:13:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.24,0:14:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at Satoh go!\NShe's soaking wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.35,0:14:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.67,0:14:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.40,0:15:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to do it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.90,0:15:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a babe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.03,0:15:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on.\NI'll find your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.00,0:15:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one else\Nwill ever find you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.93,0:15:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Breakfast!\NEverybody, fall in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.77,0:15:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.77,0:15:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when I was finally asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.78,0:15:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshioka? Where's Yoshioka?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.78,0:16:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't he come?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.11,0:16:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it,\Nhis bed wasn't slept in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.12,0:16:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That son of a bitch must've\Ngotten some by himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.79,0:16:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He better not have gone\Nafter Kayo last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.08,0:16:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody look for him!\NNo, EVERYONE look for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.75,0:16:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we find him,\Nnobody gets to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.47,0:16:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yoshioka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.14,0:16:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.56,0:16:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.23,0:16:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.81,0:16:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're okay?\NTell me you're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.15,0:16:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you\Ntalking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.82,0:16:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep this quiet. Yoshioka snuck\Nover to the girls' inn last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.49,0:16:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.74,0:16:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo, you're okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.91,0:16:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.42,0:16:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was something\Nstrange, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.54,0:16:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since we came here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.01,0:17:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been hearing the\NDemon Beast calling to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.51,0:17:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.\NThat thing's gone from this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.35,0:17:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. But I hear it.\NIs it my imagination?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.98,0:17:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.73,0:17:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe being in a strange\Nplace has you on edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.32,0:17:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Maybe you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.95,0:17:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it. Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.70,0:17:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you're used to this place,\Nyou'll feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor! Professor!\NYoshioka's... It's horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.04,0:17:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Kamimura?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.79,0:17:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's... He's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.05,0:17:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.35,0:17:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.73,0:17:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, somebody's\Nsliced his... thing off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.07,0:18:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.82,0:18:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't have anything\Nto do with the Demon Beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.41,0:18:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.74,0:18:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Demon Beast is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.38,0:18:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you all to stand\Nby with your luggage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.09,0:18:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, the police!\NYou have to call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.05,0:18:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but we don't\Nhave a phone on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.06,0:18:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A radio, then!\NSurely you have a radio!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.06,0:18:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... It's broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.06,0:18:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then from somebody else's house!\NThis is a murder, for God's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.77,0:18:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.11,0:18:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They may not want to help if it\Nmeans scaring the tourists away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.41,0:18:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the boat! When does\Nthe ferry come back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.12,0:18:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the day you\Nscheduled it to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.08,0:18:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I even ask?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.79,0:19:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.76,0:19:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.05,0:19:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forget\Nhow this feels!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.40,0:19:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More! More!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.40,0:20:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor thing.\NShe wasn't your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.45,0:20:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got that?! You keep the\Ndoors bolted when you sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.87,0:20:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially the girls!\NDon't unlock them for anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.58,0:20:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, for the boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many of you have the\Nguts and brains to volunteer...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.92,0:20:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to form into teams\Nto patrol the area?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.18,0:20:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Ungyosai!\N- Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I will guard the\Ngirls' compound tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.56,0:20:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time we'll find\Nyour real mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.56,0:21:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.94,0:21:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until your parts bring her to you,\Nyou must hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.26,0:21:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto, can't we leave it like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.59,0:21:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to call you back if\Nsomething happens here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.89,0:21:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.93,0:22:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What good's a lock when the\Nwindow's wide open?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.56,0:22:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do anything about it.\NNone of the windows here lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.98,0:22:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess nothing like this has\Never happened on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.98,0:22:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.65,0:22:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I guess we're the ones who\Nbrought trouble to paradise!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.24,0:22:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean that.\NI didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.30,0:22:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, switch off!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.01,0:22:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ungyosai! Now that you've\Nhad your bath, meal, and nap...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.26,0:22:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...grab your rain gear and get\Nover here! Three-hour shifts!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.72,0:22:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.93,0:22:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest of you, go to bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.02,0:22:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.02,0:22:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think it's the\Nmonster's revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.69,0:22:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out! You want to\Nsleep or don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.28,0:22:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be the Demon Beast...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.32,0:23:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It couldn't be!\NIt's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.31,0:23:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like some sort of fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.73,0:23:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.07,0:23:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting\Nfor this chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.41,0:23:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to\Nmake love to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.39,0:24:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you! I love you!\NI LOVE YOU!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.80,0:24:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mustn't let you\Ninterfere with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.20,0:25:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.20,0:25:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.88,0:26:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.93,0:26:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.27,0:26:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.52,0:26:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.90,0:26:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fucking little...!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.53,0:26:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.83,0:26:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.25,0:26:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.42,0:26:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.26,0:26:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.97,0:26:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! I can't\Ntake this anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.19,0:26:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.36,0:27:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Beast, begone!\NTake this!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.29,0:27:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.96,0:27:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.67,0:27:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto! Take Kayo\Nand get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.34,0:27:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.06,0:27:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interplanetary Mutual Observation\NAgency Demon Beast Buster.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.27,0:27:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Code name: Irimote.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.98,0:27:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.31,0:27:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the Demon Beast's...\NIt's come back to life again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.36,0:27:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain in detail later.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.03,0:27:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless we get Kayo away from it,\Nwe can't stop its resurrection!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.57,0:27:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take Kayo with you and head\Nfor the northern promontory!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.33,0:27:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.34,0:28:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.38,0:28:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.02,0:28:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's her...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.69,0:28:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl... The mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.66,0:28:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo! Kayo!\NAre you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.70,0:28:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.66,0:28:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind me...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.37,0:28:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's gotten\Ncaught in this nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.42,0:28:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault!\NWhat do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.34,0:28:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?!\NWhat do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.38,0:28:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down! Get a hold\Nof yourself, Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.64,0:28:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.39,0:28:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one\Nthe Demon Beast wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.06,0:29:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you lose your head,\Nhe'll take you for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.65,0:29:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.45,0:29:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glad I caught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.74,0:29:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Demon Beast... It wasn't\Ndestroyed completely?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.75,0:29:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it was. But its\Nsoul has returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.42,0:29:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.38,0:29:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should know by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.34,0:29:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing has life and healing\Npower beyond any human's.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.44,0:29:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.82,0:29:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The soul of the\Ndead Demon Beast...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.16,0:30:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...floated bodiless\Nin the void of space.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.75,0:30:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it couldn't forget the\Nsmell of Kayo's womb.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.42,0:30:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Particles of it collected\Non a meteor bound for Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.76,0:30:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and, unknown to anyone,\Nreturned them to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.77,0:30:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The particles containing its\Nmemories dissolved into the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.77,0:30:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the El Niño effect\Nallowed enough of them to gather...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.78,0:30:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to be reborn\Nin a suitable form.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.16,0:30:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something a bit like\Na sea anemone
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.75,0:30:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying it came to\Nthis island to wait for Kayo?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.17,0:30:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It possesses precognitive\Npowers ten thousand times...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.89,0:31:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...more sensitive than a whale's\Nhearing from pole to pole.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.18,0:31:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It foresaw Kayo coming here\Nand prepared to be reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.15,0:31:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.90,0:31:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kayo and the others were\Nattacked by Demon Beast larvae.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.19,0:31:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You saw them!\N- Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.74,0:31:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why was Kayo the\Nonly one they didn't latch on to?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.20,0:31:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it still\Ntrusts its mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.87,0:31:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It threatens to turn the\Nworld into hell itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.54,0:31:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it gains control of Kayo's womb,\Nit will gain enormous power.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.55,0:31:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough to be reborn\Nas the devil himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.21,0:31:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.63,0:31:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the Beast is\Nsomewhere near this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.89,0:31:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. So we have to kill it\Nbefore it can have Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.23,0:31:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To prepare for its rebirth,\Nthe Demon Beast needs sustenance.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.61,0:31:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The larvae that attacked\Nthe girls at the inn...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.24,0:32:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...have probably taken\Nthem back to their king.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.91,0:32:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.83,0:32:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're just like ants or bees.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.29,0:32:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're drones, clones with the\Ngenetic information of their king.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.50,0:32:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think of them as parts of the\Nentire horrible Demon Beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.34,0:32:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea monster on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.22,0:32:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure this isn't it?\NMaybe it isn't the Demon Beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.23,0:32:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Accept reality. They were\Ncalling Kayo mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.77,0:32:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.03,0:32:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do? If that\Nmonster is fully reborn...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.62,0:32:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it wouldn't stop with\Nthe people on this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.20,0:32:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Japan... The whole world\Nwould be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.71,0:32:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to remember, Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.25,0:32:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've beaten it so far by\Ninvoking the power of Maitreya!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.26,0:33:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a shrine to Maitreya built\Nby ancient Chinese monks...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.97,0:33:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...on the cliffs of this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.01,0:33:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Maitreya statue?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.60,0:33:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reach those\Nheights again, Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.60,0:33:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you and Kayo give your bodies\Nover to the summit of passion...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.35,0:33:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Maitreya's great power\Nwill be released.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.32,0:33:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you can defeat\Nthe Demon Beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.19,0:33:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.32,0:33:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! I love Kayo!\NI can do it anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.70,0:33:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I... I'm not exactly\Nin the mood right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.66,0:33:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you\Ntalking about, Kayo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.71,0:33:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our happiness\Ncan save the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.34,0:33:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls feel a little more\Nnaive about these things...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.34,0:33:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't make love to you\Nat a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.26,0:33:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.68,0:33:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.06,0:33:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...\NI don't believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.69,0:33:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's get to\Nthe Maitreya shrine!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.36,0:34:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Right!\N- Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.73,0:34:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Landslide.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.15,0:34:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't a recent one, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.07,0:34:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometime before, a typhoon\Nmust have collapsed the cliff...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.41,0:34:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...along with the statue.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.12,0:34:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.08,0:34:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.66,0:34:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably sunk into the\Nbeach by the coral reef.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.42,0:34:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start looking for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.46,0:35:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Irimote!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.05,0:35:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.72,0:35:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you\Ntouch my child!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.10,0:35:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.72,0:35:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... You're its mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.44,0:35:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I envy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.44,0:35:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.77,0:35:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back off, pal!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.07,0:35:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.45,0:35:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found the child. And I\Nraised it like it was my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.83,0:35:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was its mother... I was!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.08,0:35:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, the day you\Ncame to this island...!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.13,0:35:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the days of joy\Nwe shared were ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.51,0:35:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The joy between us...\NThe child and me!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.86,0:36:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.45,0:36:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.50,0:36:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!\NMother comes! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.09,0:36:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.17,0:36:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm your mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.51,0:36:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.51,0:36:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?\NAin't I your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.52,0:36:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MOTHER!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.45,0:36:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so lonely...\NHeartbroken!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.79,0:37:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was their mother,\Nwho was to raise them.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.87,0:37:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was\Nto be someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.80,0:37:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was you, Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.47,0:37:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know\Nwhat you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.60,0:37:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing you're protecting\Nis a horrible Demon Beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.14,0:37:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the poor sea monster,\Nwho's returned to the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.90,0:37:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I welcomed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.19,0:37:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It's not the creature\Nfrom that sad old legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.24,0:37:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a devil, bent on\Ndestroying the entire world!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.20,0:37:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A devil, huh? Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.24,0:37:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may not like it,\Nbut as its follower...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.75,0:37:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I have to bring Kayo to it!\NKayo, prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.92,0:37:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.92,0:37:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.85,0:38:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may not like it...\NBut she is its mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.65,0:38:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will do as it wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.87,0:38:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.92,0:38:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother! Power!\NGive me your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.92,0:39:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gasp with pleasure!\NCry out in delight!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.67,0:39:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really so joyful\Nat my rebirth?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.98,0:39:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More pleasure! This is\Nyour true nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.69,0:39:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then soon, soon...\NYou will overflow!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.29,0:39:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Playthings!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.63,0:39:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll suck\Nit all from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.00,0:39:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll drain all\Nyour love juices...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.38,0:40:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and then join you all\Ninto my own body!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.69,0:40:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!\NMother, where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.07,0:40:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.78,0:40:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.79,0:40:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! Your mother,\Njust like you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.37,0:40:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do what you want with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.67,0:40:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! Take the\Nimmortal love from her!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.09,0:40:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.72,0:40:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.77,0:40:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.74,0:41:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother! Oh, your scent!\NAh, how wet you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.12,0:41:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How happy you are\Nto see me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.79,0:41:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, joyous day! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.46,0:41:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me more. More!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.46,0:41:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How it wriggles,\Nhow it must wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.14,0:41:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been\Nwaiting too, Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.72,0:41:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you desired me as well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.48,0:41:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I will do as I wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.40,0:41:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.41,0:41:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.08,0:41:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Don't let them escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.84,0:42:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.34,0:42:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo, while I'm drawing\Nhim off from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.89,0:42:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you run for if\Nfrom the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.85,0:42:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.20,0:42:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.81,0:42:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The statue of Maitreya!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.91,0:43:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Kayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.08,0:43:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.15,0:44:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto! Muneto!\NOh, yes! YES!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.27,0:45:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.63,0:45:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was a strange girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.59,0:45:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.93,0:45:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she'll live on, just\Nanother legend for this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.81,0:45:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think, maybe... Maybe\NI understand how she felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.32,0:45:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.98,0:45:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo, I'd never let anything\Ntake you from me, ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.32,0:45:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto...
